Step runner with live collapsing output в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n    51вҶ’#\n    52вҶ’# Shows a scrolling window of the last N output lines while running.\n    53вҶ’# When the step finishes, erases the log and collapses to one status line.\n    54вҶ’#\n    55вҶ’step() {\n    56вҶ’    local msg=\"$1\"\n    57вҶ’    shift\n    58вҶ’    CURRENT_STEP=$((CURRENT_STEP + 1))\n    59вҶ’\n    60вҶ’    local tmpout=\"/tmp/deploy-step-$$\"\n    61вҶ’    local rcfile=\"/tmp/deploy-rc-$$\"\n    62вҶ’    local max_visible=8\n    63вҶ’    local trunc_width\n    64вҶ’    trunc_width=$(( $(tput cols 2>/dev/null || echo 80) - 6 ))\n    65вҶ’\n    66вҶ’    > \"$tmpout\"\n    67вҶ’    rm -f \"$rcfile\"\n    68вҶ’\n    69вҶ’    # Print header\n    70вҶ’    printf \"  ${DIM}[%d/%d]${RESET} ${CYAN}в—Ҹ${RESET} %s\\n\" \"$CURRENT_STEP\" \"$TOTAL_STEPS\" \"$msg\"\n    71вҶ’\n    72вҶ’    # Run command in background, save exit code\n    73вҶ’    ( set +e; \"$@\" >> \"$tmpout\" 2>&1; echo \"$?\" > \"$rcfile\" ) &\n    74вҶ’    local cmd_pid=$!\n    75вҶ’\n    76вҶ’    tput civis 2>/dev/null || true  # hide cursor\n    77вҶ’\n    78вҶ’    local prev_lines=0\n    79вҶ’\n    80вҶ’    while kill -0 \"$cmd_pid\" 2>/dev/null; do\n    81вҶ’        # Erase previously drawn output lines\n    82вҶ’        if [[ $prev_lines -gt 0 ]]; then\n    83вҶ’            printf \"\\033[%dA\\033[J\" \"$prev_lines\"\n    84вҶ’        fi\n    85вҶ’\n    86вҶ’        # Draw last N lines from output\n    87вҶ’        prev_lines=0\n    88вҶ’        if [[ -s \"$tmpout\" ]]; then\n    89вҶ’            while IFS= read -r line; do\n    90вҶ’                printf \"    ${DIM}%.*s${RESET}\\n\" \"$trunc_width\" \"$line\"\n    91вҶ’                prev_lines=$((prev_lines + 1))\n    92вҶ’            done < <(tail -n \"$max_visible\" \"$tmpout\")\n    93вҶ’        fi\n    94вҶ’\n    95вҶ’        sleep 0.15\n    96вҶ’    done\n    97вҶ’    wait \"$cmd_pid\" 2>/dev/null || true\n    98вҶ’\n    99вҶ’    # Erase log lines + header\n   100вҶ’    local erase=$((prev_lines + 1))\n   101вҶ’    printf \"\\033[%dA\\033[J\" \"$erase\"\n   102вҶ’\n   103вҶ’    tput cnorm 2>/dev/null || true  # show cursor\n   104вҶ’\n   105вҶ’    local rc\n   106вҶ’    rc=$(cat \"$rcfile\" 2>/dev/null || echo 1)\n   107вҶ’\n   108вҶ’    if [[ \"$rc\" -eq 0 ]]; then\n   109вҶ’        printf \"  ${DIM}[%d/%d]${RESET} ${GREEN}${TICK}${RESET} %s\\n\" \"$CURRENT_STEP\" \"$TOTAL_STEPS\" \"$msg\"\n   110вҶ’    else\n   111вҶ’        printf \"  ${DIM}[%d/%d]${RESET} ${RED}${CROSS}${RESET} %s\\n\" \"$CURRENT_STEP\" \"$TOTAL_STEPS\" \"$msg\"\n   112вҶ’        echo \"\"\n   113вҶ’        printf \"  ${RED}${BOLD}Error:${RESET} Step failed. Last 20 lines:\\n\\n\"\n   114вҶ’        tail -20 \"$tmpout\" | sed 's/^/    /'\n   115вҶ’        echo \"\"\n   116вҶ’        printf \"  ${DIM}Full log: %s${RESET}\\n\" \"$LOG_FILE\"\n   117вҶ’        cat \"$tmpout\" >> \"$LOG_FILE\"\n   118вҶ’        exit 1\n   119вҶ’    fi\n   120вҶ’\n   121вҶ’    cat \"$tmpout\" >> \"$LOG_FILE\"\n   122вҶ’    rm -f \"$tmpout\" \"$rcfile\"\n   123вҶ’}\n   124вҶ’\n   125вҶ’# в”Җв”Җв”Җ Prerequisite checks в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n   126вҶ’check_deps() {\n   127вҶ’    if ! command -v docker &>/dev/null; then\n   128вҶ’        printf \"  ${RED}${BOLD}Missing dependency:${RESET} docker\\n\\n\"\n   129вҶ’        printf \"  Install Docker: https://docs.docker.com/get-docker/\\n\\n\"\n   130вҶ’        exit 1\n   131вҶ’    fi\n   132вҶ’}\n   133вҶ’\n   134вҶ’# в”Җв”Җв”Җ Remote helpers в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n   135вҶ’remote() {\n   136вҶ’    $SSH_CMD \"$@\"\n   137вҶ’}\n   138вҶ’\n   139вҶ’remote_scp() {\n   140вҶ’    scp -i \"$DEPLOY_KEY\" -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no -o LogLevel=ERROR -o BatchMode=yes \"$@\"\n   141вҶ’}\n   142вҶ’\n   143вҶ’# в”Җв”Җв”Җ Step implementations в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n   144вҶ’\n   145вҶ’do_install_docker() {\n   146вҶ’    remote bash -s <<'SCRIPT'\n   147вҶ’if command -v docker &>/dev/null; then\n   148вҶ’    echo \"Docker already installed: $(docker --version)\"\n   149вҶ’    systemctl start docker 2>/dev/null || service docker start 2>/dev/null || true\n   150вҶ’    exit 0\n   151вҶ’fi\n   152вҶ’\n   153вҶ’echo \"Installing Docker...\"\n   154вҶ’export DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive\n   155вҶ’\n   156вҶ’curl -fsSL https://get.docker.com | sh\n   157вҶ’\n   158вҶ’systemctl enable docker 2>/dev/null || true\n   159вҶ’systemctl start docker 2>/dev/null || service docker start 2>/dev/null || true\n   160вҶ’\n   161вҶ’usermod -aG docker \"$(whoami)\" 2>/dev/null || true\n   162вҶ’\n   163вҶ’echo \"Docker installed: $(docker --version)\"\n   164вҶ’SCRIPT\n   165вҶ’}\n   166вҶ’\n   167вҶ’do_build_images() {\n   168вҶ’    echo \"Building desent-server image...\"\n   169вҶ’    docker build --platform linux/amd64 -t desent-server .\n   170вҶ’\n   171вҶ’    echo \"Building desent-web image...\"\n   172вҶ’    docker build --platform linux/amd64 -t desent-web ./web/liches-web\n   173вҶ’}\n   174вҶ’\n   175вҶ’do_transfer_images() {\n   176вҶ’    echo \"Saving and transferring desent-server...\"\n   177вҶ’    docker save desent-server | $SSH_CMD \"docker load\"\n   178вҶ’\n   179вҶ’    echo \"Saving and transferring desent-web...\"\n   180вҶ’    docker save desent-web | $SSH_CMD \"docker load\"\n   181вҶ’}\n   182вҶ’\n   183вҶ’do_generate_config() {\n   184вҶ’    local jwt_secret\n   185вҶ’    jwt_secret=$(openssl rand -hex 32)\n   186вҶ’\n   187вҶ’    cat > /tmp/deploy-compose-$$ <<YAML\n   188вҶ’services:\n   189вҶ’  traefik:\n   190вҶ’    image: traefik:v3.3\n   191вҶ’    command:\n   192вҶ’      - --api.insecure=true\n   193вҶ’      - --providers.docker=true\n   194вҶ’      - --providers.docker.exposedbydefault=false\n   195вҶ’      - --entrypoints.web.address=:80\n   196вҶ’    ports:\n   197вҶ’      - \"80:80\"\n   198вҶ’      - \"8080:8080\"\n   199вҶ’    volumes:\n   200вҶ’      - /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock:ro\n   201вҶ’    restart: unless-stopped\n   202вҶ’\n   203вҶ’  server:\n   204вҶ’    image: desent-server:latest\n   205вҶ’    labels:\n   206вҶ’      - traefik.enable=true\n   207вҶ’      - \"traefik.http.routers.api.rule=PathPrefix(\\`/api\\`) || PathPrefix(\\`/ws\\`) || PathPrefix(\\`/live\\`) || PathPrefix(\\`/health\\`)\"\n   208вҶ’      - traefik.http.routers.api.entrypoints=web\n   209вҶ’      - traefik.http.services.api.loadbalancer.server.port=8080\n   210вҶ’    ports:\n   211вҶ’      - \"1935:1935\"\n   212вҶ’    environment:\n   213вҶ’      - JWT_SECRET=${jwt_secret}\n   214вҶ’      - STREAM_KEY=live\n   215вҶ’      - DB_PATH=/data/desent.db\n   216вҶ’      - HLS_DIR=/tmp/hls\n   217вҶ’      - HTTP_ADDR=:8080\n   218вҶ’      - RTMP_ADDR=0.0.0.0:1935\n   219вҶ’    volumes:\n   220вҶ’      - db-data:/data\n   221вҶ’    restart: unless-stopped\n   222вҶ’\n   223вҶ’  web:\n   224вҶ’    image: desent-web:latest\n   225вҶ’    labels:\n   226вҶ’      - traefik.enable=true\n   227вҶ’      - \"traefik.http.routers.web.rule=PathPrefix(\\`/\\`)\"\n   228вҶ’      - traefik.http.routers.web.entrypoints=web\n   229вҶ’      - traefik.http.routers.web.priority=1\n   230вҶ’      - traefik.http.services.web.loadbalancer.server.port=3000\n   231вҶ’    environment:\n   232вҶ’      - NEXT_PUBLIC_BACKEND_URL=http://${SERVER_IP}\n   233вҶ’    depends_on:\n   234вҶ’      - server\n   235вҶ’    restart: unless-stopped\n   236вҶ’\n   237вҶ’volumes:\n   238вҶ’  db-data:\n   239вҶ’YAML\n   240вҶ’\n   241вҶ’    echo \"Creating /opt/desent on server...\"\n   242вҶ’    remote mkdir -p /opt/desent\n   243вҶ’\n   244вҶ’    echo \"Uploading docker-compose.yml...\"\n   245вҶ’    remote_scp /tmp/deploy-compose-$$ \"${SSH_TARGET}:/opt/desent/docker-compose.yml\"\n   246вҶ’\n   247вҶ’    rm -f /tmp/deploy-compose-$$\n   248вҶ’    echo \"Config deployed.\"\n   249вҶ’}\n   250вҶ’\n   251вҶ’do_deploy() {\n   252вҶ’    remote bash -s <<'SCRIPT'\n   253вҶ’cd /opt/desent\n   254вҶ’\n   255вҶ’echo \"Stopping old containers...\"\n   256вҶ’docker compose down 2>/dev/null || true\n   257вҶ’\n   258вҶ’echo \"Starting containers...\"\n   259вҶ’docker compose up -d\n   260вҶ’\n   261вҶ’echo \"Containers running:\"\n   262вҶ’docker compose ps\n   263вҶ’SCRIPT\n   264вҶ’}\n   265вҶ’\n   266вҶ’do_verify() {\n   267вҶ’    local max_attempts=30\n   268вҶ’    local attempt=0\n   269вҶ’\n   270вҶ’    echo \"Waiting for health check...\"\n   271вҶ’    while [[ $attempt -lt $max_attempts ]]; do\n   272вҶ’        if remote curl -sf -o /dev/null \"http://127.0.0.1/health\" 2>/dev/null; then\n   273вҶ’            echo \"Health check passed!\"\n   274вҶ’            return 0\n   275вҶ’        fi\n   276вҶ’        attempt=$((attempt + 1))\n   277вҶ’        echo \"  attempt $attempt/$max_attempts...\"\n   278вҶ’        sleep 2\n   279вҶ’    done\n   280вҶ’\n   281вҶ’    echo \"Health check did not pass after ${max_attempts} attempts.\"\n   282вҶ’    echo \"Check: ${SSH_CMD} 'cd /opt/desent && docker compose logs'\"\n   283вҶ’    return 1\n   284вҶ’}\n   285вҶ’\n   286вҶ’# в”Җв”Җв”Җ Main в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\n   287вҶ’main() {\n   288вҶ’    banner\n   289вҶ’    check_deps\n   290вҶ’\n   291вҶ’    # Prompt for SSH target\n   292вҶ’    printf \"  ${BOLD}How do you SSH into the server?${RESET}\\n\"\n   293вҶ’    printf \"  ${DIM}Example: ssh root@1.2.3.4${RESET}\\n\\n\"\n   294вҶ’\n   295вҶ’    read -rp \"  > \" SSH_INPUT\n   296вҶ’    [[ -z \"$SSH_INPUT\" ]] && fatal \"SSH command is required\"\n   297вҶ’\n   298вҶ’    # Normalize: add \"ssh\" prefix if user just typed \"root@1.2.3.4\"\n   299вҶ’    if [[ \"$SSH_INPUT\" != ssh\\ * ]]; then\n   300вҶ’        SSH_INPUT=\"ssh $SSH_INPUT\"\n   301вҶ’    fi\n   302вҶ’\n   303вҶ’    # Extract user@host (last argument) for scp and display\n   304вҶ’    SSH_TARGET=\"${SSH_INPUT##* }\"\n   305вҶ’    SERVER_IP=\"${SSH_TARGET#*@}\"\n   306вҶ’\n   307вҶ’    # в”Җв”Җ Setup deploy key (no passphrase, fully automated) в”Җв”Җ\n   308вҶ’    echo \"\"\n   309вҶ’    if [[ ! -f \"$DEPLOY_KEY\" ]]; then\n   310вҶ’        printf \"  ${DIM}Generating deploy key (no passphrase)...${RESET}\\n\"\n   311вҶ’        ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -f \"$DEPLOY_KEY\" -N \"\" -q -C \"desent-deploy\"\n   312вҶ’        printf \"  ${GREEN}${TICK}${RESET} Created %s\\n\" \"$DEPLOY_KEY\"\n   313вҶ’    fi\n   314вҶ’\n   315вҶ’    # Check if deploy key already works\n   316вҶ’    if ssh -i \"$DEPLOY_KEY\" -o BatchMode=yes -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no -o ConnectTimeout=5 -o LogLevel=ERROR \\\n   317вҶ’        \"$SSH_TARGET\" true 2>/dev/null; then\n   318вҶ’        printf \"  ${GREEN}${TICK}${RESET} Deploy key already on server\\n\"\n   319вҶ’    else\n   320вҶ’        # Copy deploy key using user's normal SSH (interactive вҖ” password/passphrase OK)\n   321вҶ’        printf \"  ${DIM}Installing deploy key on server (you may need to enter password):${RESET}\\n\"\n   322вҶ’        local pubkey\n   323вҶ’        pubkey=$(cat \"${DEPLOY_KEY}.pub\")\n   324вҶ’        $SSH_INPUT -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no -o ConnectTimeout=10 \\\n   325вҶ’            \"mkdir -p ~/.ssh && chmod 700 ~/.ssh && echo '${pubkey}' >> ~/.ssh/authorized_keys && chmod 600 ~/.ssh/authorized_keys\" \\\n   326вҶ’            || fatal \"Failed to install deploy key. Make sure you can run: $SSH_INPUT\"\n   327вҶ’        printf \"  ${GREEN}${TICK}${RESET} Deploy key installed\\n\"\n   328вҶ’    fi\n   329вҶ’\n   330вҶ’    # From here on, use the deploy key only вҖ” no prompts, no passphrases\n   331вҶ’    SSH_CMD=\"ssh -i ${DEPLOY_KEY} -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no -o ConnectTimeout=10 -o LogLevel=ERROR -o BatchMode=yes ${SSH_TARGET}\"\n   332вҶ’\n   333вҶ’    # Verify it works\n   334вҶ’    if ! $SSH_CMD true 2>/dev/null; then\n   335вҶ’        fatal \"Deploy key not working. Try: rm ${DEPLOY_KEY}* && ./deploy.sh\"\n   336вҶ’    fi\n   337вҶ’\n   338вҶ’    printf \"\\n  ${DIM}Deploying to ${BOLD}%s${RESET}\\n\\n\" \"$SSH_TARGET\"\n   339вҶ’\n   340вҶ’    # Run steps\n   341вҶ’    step \"Installing Docker\"          do_install_docker\n   342вҶ’    step \"Building Docker images\"     do_build_images\n   343вҶ’    step \"Transferring images\"        do_transfer_images\n   344вҶ’    step \"Generating config\"          do_generate_config\n   345вҶ’    step \"Deploying containers\"       do_deploy\n   346вҶ’    step \"Verifying deployment\"       do_verify\n   347вҶ’\n   348вҶ’    # Done\n   349вҶ’    echo \"\"\n   350вҶ’    printf \"  ${GREEN}${BOLD}${TICK} Deploy complete!${RESET}\\n\"\n   351вҶ’    echo \"\"\n   352вҶ’    printf \"  ${BOLD}Web app:${RESET}     http://%s\\n\" \"$SERVER_IP\"\n   353вҶ’    printf \"  ${BOLD}RTMP ingest:${RESET} rtmp://%s:1935/live/live\\n\" \"$SERVER_IP\"\n   354вҶ’    printf \"  ${BOLD}Traefik:${RESET}     http://%s:8080\\n\" \"$SERVER_IP\"\n   355вҶ’    echo \"\"\n   356вҶ’    printf \"  ${DIM}Stream with OBS вҶ’ rtmp://%s:1935/live/live${RESET}\\n\" \"$SERVER_IP\"\n   357вҶ’    printf \"  ${DIM}Watch at вҶ’ http://%s${RESET}\\n\" \"$SERVER_IP\"\n   358вҶ’    echo \"\"\n   359вҶ’}\n   360вҶ’\n   361вҶ’main \"$@\"\n   362вҶ’",
