          "text": "     1вҶ’# Decentralized Twitch (twitch-desent)\n     2вҶ’\n     3вҶ’## Project Overview\n     4вҶ’\n     5вҶ’Decentralized streaming platform where **streamers self-host their own servers**. The platform provides either a ready-to-deploy binary (streamer buys domain + VPS, enters data in our installer app like Amnezia, we auto-configure everything) or a managed cloud option (with content moderation вҖ” no pirated movies/casinos).\n     6вҶ’\n     7вҶ’### Key Concept\n     8вҶ’Each streamer runs their own Go server (single binary). They can:\n     9вҶ’- Add Edge CDN nodes for geo-coverage (e.g., Novosibirsk, St. Petersburg)\n    10вҶ’- Host other streamers on their server\n    11вҶ’- Register in a Discovery catalog (after moderation) so new viewers can find them\n    12вҶ’\n    13вҶ’## Architecture\n    14вҶ’\n    15вҶ’### Video Pipeline\n    16вҶ’```\n    17вҶ’OBS вҶ’ RTMP (:1935) вҶ’ FFmpeg (1080pвҶ’720pвҶ’480pвҶ’360p) вҶ’ HLS segments (2-4 sec) вҶ’ HTTP delivery (:443)\n    18вҶ’```\n    19вҶ’\n    20вҶ’### Components (Single Binary)\n    21вҶ’- **RTMP Ingest** вҖ” accepts OBS stream on port 1935\n    22вҶ’- **FFmpeg Transcoder** вҖ” multi-quality HLS segmentation\n    23вҶ’- **HLS Delivery** вҖ” serves `.m3u8` playlists and `.ts` segments via HTTP\n    24вҶ’- **WebSocket Chat** вҖ” 1 dispatcher goroutine, broadcast to all viewers, rooms per stream\n    25вҶ’- **Auth** вҖ” JWT-based, middleware on all endpoints\n    26вҶ’- **Admin API** вҖ” stream settings, CDN node management, user/ban management\n    27вҶ’- **SQLite** вҖ” local database for users, bans, settings, logs\n    28вҶ’\n    29вҶ’### External Services (NOT in MVP)\n    30вҶ’- **Discovery Service** вҖ” cloud catalog of trusted servers (PostgreSQL, moderation)\n    31вҶ’- **Edge Nodes** вҖ” Go binaries that cache HLS segments from origin server\n    32вҶ’\n    33вҶ’## Tech Stack\n    34вҶ’\n    35вҶ’- **Language:** Go 1.23\n    36вҶ’- **Database:** SQLite (via `modernc.org/sqlite` вҖ” pure Go, no CGO)\n    37вҶ’- **HTTP Router:** `net/http` (stdlib, Go 1.22+ routing)\n    38вҶ’- **WebSocket:** `nhooyr.io/websocket`\n    39вҶ’- **JWT:** `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5`\n    40вҶ’- **RTMP:** `github.com/nareix/joy5` or custom RTMP listener\n    41вҶ’- **Video:** FFmpeg (external process, managed via `os/exec`)\n    42вҶ’- **Config:** Environment variables + YAML config file\n    43вҶ’\n    44вҶ’## Project Structure\n    45вҶ’\n    46вҶ’```\n    47вҶ’twitch-desent/\n    48вҶ’в”ңв”Җв”Җ cmd/\n    49вҶ’в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ server/\n    50вҶ’в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ main.go              # Entry point, wires everything together\n    51вҶ’в”ңв”Җв”Җ internal/\n    52вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ config/\n    53вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ config.go            # App configuration (env vars only)\n    54вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ auth/\n    55вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ handler.go           # POST /api/auth/register, POST /api/auth/login\n    56вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ jwt.go               # JWT generation & validation (Claims struct, TokenService)\n    57вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ middleware.go         # Auth middleware (extracts user from token)\n    58вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ store.go             # User storage (SQLite-backed, first user = admin)\n    59вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ chat/\n    60вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ hub.go               # Central dispatcher (1 goroutine), session tracking\n    61вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ client.go            # Per-connection read/write pumps (nhooyr.io/websocket)\n    62вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ handler.go           # WS upgrade endpoint + chat history REST API\n    63вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ store.go             # stream_sessions + chat_messages CRUD\n    64вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ ingest/\n    65вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ manager.go           # FFmpeg subprocess lifecycle, IsLive() status\n    66вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ ffmpeg.go            # FFmpeg CLI args builder\n    67вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ hls/\n    68вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ handler.go           # Serves HLS playlists/segments, stream status endpoint\n    69вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ cleaner.go           # Periodic cleanup of old HLS segments\n    70вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ admin/\n    71вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ handler.go           # Admin-only API: settings, bans, CDN config\n    72вҶ’в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ db/\n    73вҶ’в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ sqlite.go            # Dual-pool DB (write=1 conn, read=4 conns), WAL mode\n    74вҶ’в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ migrations.go        # Schema creation (users, settings, stream_sessions, chat_messages)\n    75вҶ’в”ңв”Җв”Җ static/\n    76вҶ’в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ player.html              # hls.js test player\n    77вҶ’в”ңв”Җв”Җ Dockerfile                   # Multi-stage: golang:1.24-alpine вҶ’ alpine:3.21 + ffmpeg\n    78вҶ’в”ңв”Җв”Җ docker-compose.yml           # Ports 8080 (HTTP) + 1935 (RTMP)\n    79вҶ’в”ңв”Җв”Җ CLAUDE.md\n    80вҶ’в”ңв”Җв”Җ TODO.md\n    81вҶ’в”ңв”Җв”Җ go.mod\n    82вҶ’в””в”Җв”Җ go.sum\n    83вҶ’```\n    84вҶ’\n    85вҶ’## API Endpoints (MVP)\n    86вҶ’\n    87вҶ’### Auth (no auth required)\n    88вҶ’- `POST /api/auth/register` вҖ” `{username, password}` вҶ’ creates user, returns JWT\n    89вҶ’- `POST /api/auth/login` вҖ” `{username, password}` вҶ’ validates, returns JWT\n    90вҶ’\n    91вҶ’### Stream (auth required for some)\n    92вҶ’- `GET /live/{quality}/playlist.m3u8` вҖ” HLS master/variant playlist (public)\n    93вҶ’- `GET /live/{quality}/{segment}.ts` вҖ” HLS segment file (public)\n    94вҶ’- `GET /api/stream/status` вҖ” current stream info (public)\n    95вҶ’\n    96вҶ’### Chat\n    97вҶ’- `WS /ws/chat?token=JWT` вҖ” WebSocket connection (auth required, token in query param)\n    98вҶ’- `GET /api/chat/history/{sessionId}?limit=50&before=messageId` вҖ” chat history (public)\n    99вҶ’- `GET /api/chat/sessions?limit=20` вҖ” list stream sessions (public)\n   100вҶ’\n   101вҶ’### Admin (admin auth required)\n   102вҶ’- `GET /api/admin/settings` вҖ” get server settings\n   103вҶ’- `PUT /api/admin/settings` вҖ” update server settings\n   104вҶ’- `GET /api/admin/users` вҖ” list users\n   105вҶ’- `POST /api/admin/ban` вҖ” ban a user\n   106вҶ’- `DELETE /api/admin/ban/{userId}` вҖ” unban\n   107вҶ’\n   108вҶ’## Development Commands\n   109вҶ’\n   110вҶ’```bash\n   111вҶ’# Run the server\n   112вҶ’go run ./cmd/server\n   113вҶ’\n   114вҶ’# Build single binary\n   115вҶ’go build -o desent-server ./cmd/server\n   116вҶ’\n   117вҶ’# Run tests\n   118вҶ’go test ./...\n   119вҶ’\n   120вҶ’# Run with race detector\n   121вҶ’go test -race ./...\n   122вҶ’```\n   123вҶ’\n   124вҶ’## MVP Scope\n   125вҶ’\n   126вҶ’Building the **streamer server only** (single binary). Mocked auth with login/password (real users in SQLite, but no email verification, no OAuth вҖ” just username+passwordвҶ’JWT).\n   127вҶ’\n   128вҶ’### In Scope\n   129вҶ’- RTMP ingest + FFmpeg transcoding to HLS\n   130вҶ’- HLS segment serving (multi-quality)\n   131вҶ’- WebSocket chat with broadcast\n   132вҶ’- Auth: register/login with username+password, JWT tokens\n   133вҶ’- Admin API (REST, no UI)\n   134вҶ’- SQLite storage\n   135вҶ’\n   136вҶ’### Out of Scope (future)\n   137вҶ’- Discovery service (cloud catalog)\n   138вҶ’- Edge CDN nodes\n   139вҶ’- Admin React SPA\n   140вҶ’- OAuth / social login\n   141вҶ’- Installer/deployment scripts\n   142вҶ’- Content moderation system\n   143вҶ’\n   144вҶ’## Conventions\n   145вҶ’\n   146вҶ’- Use Go stdlib where possible (`net/http`, `log/slog`, `encoding/json`)\n   147вҶ’- Structured logging with `log/slog`\n   148вҶ’- Errors: wrap with `fmt.Errorf(\"context: %w\", err)`\n   149вҶ’- No frameworks вҖ” keep dependencies minimal\n   150вҶ’- Tests alongside code (`*_test.go` in same package)\n   151вҶ’- Context propagation through all handlers\n   152вҶ’- Graceful shutdown on SIGINT/SIGTERM\n   153вҶ’\n   154вҶ’## Codebase Patterns\n   155вҶ’\n   156вҶ’### Module Wiring\n   157вҶ’Each package follows the pattern: `NewStore(db)` вҶ’ `NewHandler(store, deps)` вҶ’ `handler.RegisterRoutes(mux)`.\n   158вҶ’All wiring happens in `cmd/server/main.go`. No dependency injection framework вҖ” explicit construction.\n   159вҶ’\n   160вҶ’### Database Access\n   161вҶ’- `db.DB` has `.Write` (1 conn) and `.Read` (4 conns) pools вҖ” use Write for INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE, Read for SELECT\n   162вҶ’- SQLite with WAL mode, foreign keys enabled, 5s busy timeout\n   163вҶ’- Schema in `internal/db/migrations.go` as a single `const schema` string executed on startup\n   164вҶ’- Timestamps stored as Unix epoch integers via `DEFAULT (unixepoch())`\n   165вҶ’\n   166вҶ’### Auth Flow\n   167вҶ’- `auth.TokenService` generates/validates JWT tokens with `Claims{UserID, Username, Role}`\n   168вҶ’- First registered user auto-promoted to admin role\n   169вҶ’- WS auth: JWT passed as `?token=` query param (browser WS API can't set headers)\n   170вҶ’- HTTP auth: JWT in `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header, extracted by `auth.Middleware`\n   171вҶ’\n   172вҶ’### Chat Architecture\n   173вҶ’- Hub pattern: single goroutine event loop (select on register/unregister/broadcast/ticker/ctx.Done)\n   174вҶ’- Hub polls `ingest.Manager.IsLive()` every 2s to auto-create/close `stream_sessions`\n   175вҶ’- Messages persisted only when stream is live (sessionID > 0)\n   176вҶ’- Client has separate readPump (reads JSON from WS) and writePump (writes from send channel) goroutines\n   177вҶ’- Rate limiting: per-client, configurable via `CHAT_RATE_LIMIT_MS` (default 500ms)\n   178вҶ’- Message length cap: `CHAT_MAX_MSG_LEN` (default 500 chars, truncated silently)\n   179вҶ’- JSON wire format: `{\"type\":\"chat\"|\"system\", \"text\":\"...\", \"user_id\":N, \"username\":\"...\", \"timestamp\":N}`\n   180вҶ’\n   181вҶ’### Config\n   182вҶ’All config via environment variables with sensible defaults. `getEnv(key, fallback)` and `getEnvInt(key, fallback)` helpers.\n   183вҶ’\n   184вҶ’### Ingest/Streaming\n   185вҶ’- `ingest.Manager.Run(ctx)` вҖ” infinite loop: start FFmpeg with `-listen 1`, wait for exit, restart after 2s\n   186вҶ’