          "text": "     1вҶ’# Decentralized Twitch (twitch-desent)\n     2вҶ’\n     3вҶ’## Project Overview\n     4вҶ’\n     5вҶ’Decentralized streaming platform where **streamers self-host their own servers**. The platform provides either a ready-to-deploy binary (streamer buys domain + VPS, enters data in our installer app like Amnezia, we auto-configure everything) or a managed cloud option (with content moderation вҖ” no pirated movies/casinos).\n     6вҶ’\n     7вҶ’### Key Concept\n     8вҶ’Each streamer runs their own Go server (single binary). They can:\n     9вҶ’- Add Edge CDN nodes for geo-coverage (e.g., Novosibirsk, St. Petersburg)\n    10вҶ’- Host other streamers on their server\n    11вҶ’- Register in a Discovery catalog (after moderation) so new viewers can find them\n    12вҶ’\n    13вҶ’## Architecture\n    14вҶ’\n    15вҶ’### Video Pipeline\n    16вҶ’```\n    17вҶ’OBS вҶ’ RTMP (:1935) вҶ’ FFmpeg (1080pвҶ’720pвҶ’480pвҶ’360p) вҶ’ HLS segments (2-4 sec) вҶ’ HTTP delivery (:443)\n    18вҶ’```\n    19вҶ’\n    20вҶ’### Components (Single Binary)\n    21вҶ’- **RTMP Ingest** вҖ” accepts OBS stream on port 1935\n    22вҶ’- **FFmpeg Transcoder** вҖ” multi-quality HLS segmentation\n    23вҶ’- **HLS Delivery** вҖ” serves `.m3u8` playlists and `.ts` segments via HTTP\n    24вҶ’- **WebSocket Chat** вҖ” 1 dispatcher goroutine, broadcast to all viewers, rooms per stream\n    25вҶ’- **Auth** вҖ” JWT-based, middleware on all endpoints\n    26вҶ’- **Admin API** вҖ” stream settings, CDN node management, user/ban management\n    27вҶ’- **SQLite** вҖ” local database for users, bans, settings, logs\n    28вҶ’\n    29вҶ’### External Services (NOT in MVP)\n    30вҶ’- **Discovery Service** вҖ” cloud catalog of trusted servers (PostgreSQL, moderation)\n    31вҶ’- **Edge Nodes** вҖ” Go binaries that cache HLS segments from origin server\n    32вҶ’\n    33вҶ’## Tech Stack\n    34вҶ’\n    35вҶ’- **Language:** Go 1.23\n    36вҶ’- **Database:** SQLite (via `modernc.org/sqlite` вҖ” pure Go, no CGO)\n    37вҶ’- **HTTP Router:** `net/http` (stdlib, Go 1.22+ routing)\n    38вҶ’- **WebSocket:** `nhooyr.io/websocket`\n    39вҶ’- **JWT:** `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5`\n    40вҶ’- **RTMP:** `github.com/nareix/joy5` or custom RTMP listener\n    41вҶ’- **Video:** FFmpeg (external process, managed via `os/exec`)\n    42вҶ’- **Config:** Environment variables + YAML config file\n    43вҶ’\n    44вҶ’## Project Structure\n    45вҶ’\n    46вҶ’```\n    47вҶ’twitch-desent/\n    48вҶ’в”ңв”Җв”Җ cmd/\n    49вҶ’в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ server/\n    50вҶ’в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ main.go              # Entry point, wires everything together\n    51вҶ’в”ңв”Җв”Җ internal/\n    52вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ config/\n    53вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ config.go            # App configuration (env + yaml)\n    54вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ auth/\n    55вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ handler.go           # POST /api/auth/register, POST /api/auth/login\n    56вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ jwt.go               # JWT generation & validation\n    57вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ middleware.go         # Auth middleware (extracts user from token)\n    58вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ store.go             # User storage (SQLite-backed)\n    59вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ chat/\n    60вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ hub.go               # Central dispatcher, room management\n    61вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ client.go            # Single WebSocket connection handler\n    62вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ handler.go           # WS upgrade endpoint\n    63вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ ingest/\n    64вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ rtmp.go              # RTMP server, accepts streams\n    65вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ transcoder.go        # FFmpeg process lifecycle\n    66вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ hls/\n    67вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ handler.go           # GET /live/{quality}/playlist.m3u8, GET /live/{quality}/{segment}.ts\n    68вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ store.go             # Segment file management, cleanup\n    69вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ admin/\n    70вҶ’в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ handler.go           # Admin-only API: settings, bans, CDN config\n    71вҶ’в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ db/\n    72вҶ’в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ sqlite.go            # DB connection, initialization\n    73вҶ’в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ migrations.go        # Schema creation & migrations\n    74вҶ’в”ңв”Җв”Җ CLAUDE.md\n    75вҶ’в”ңв”Җв”Җ TODO.md\n    76вҶ’в”ңв”Җв”Җ go.mod\n    77вҶ’в””в”Җв”Җ go.sum\n    78вҶ’```\n    79вҶ’\n    80вҶ’## API Endpoints (MVP)\n    81вҶ’\n    82вҶ’### Auth (no auth required)\n    83вҶ’- `POST /api/auth/register` вҖ” `{username, password}` вҶ’ creates user, returns JWT\n    84вҶ’- `POST /api/auth/login` вҖ” `{username, password}` вҶ’ validates, returns JWT\n    85вҶ’\n    86вҶ’### Stream (auth required for some)\n    87вҶ’- `GET /live/{quality}/playlist.m3u8` вҖ” HLS master/variant playlist (public)\n    88вҶ’- `GET /live/{quality}/{segment}.ts` вҖ” HLS segment file (public)\n    89вҶ’- `GET /api/stream/status` вҖ” current stream info (public)\n    90вҶ’\n    91вҶ’### Chat (auth required)\n    92вҶ’- `WS /ws/chat` вҖ” WebSocket connection, JWT in query param or first message\n    93вҶ’\n    94вҶ’### Admin (admin auth required)\n    95вҶ’- `GET /api/admin/settings` вҖ” get server settings\n    96вҶ’- `PUT /api/admin/settings` вҖ” update server settings\n    97вҶ’- `GET /api/admin/users` вҖ” list users\n    98вҶ’- `POST /api/admin/ban` вҖ” ban a user\n    99вҶ’- `DELETE /api/admin/ban/{userId}` вҖ” unban\n   100вҶ’\n   101вҶ’## Development Commands\n   102вҶ’\n   103вҶ’```bash\n   104вҶ’# Run the server\n   105вҶ’go run ./cmd/server\n   106вҶ’\n   107вҶ’# Build single binary\n   108вҶ’go build -o desent-server ./cmd/server\n   109вҶ’\n   110вҶ’# Run tests\n   111вҶ’go test ./...\n   112вҶ’\n   113вҶ’# Run with race detector\n   114вҶ’go test -race ./...\n   115вҶ’```\n   116вҶ’\n   117вҶ’## MVP Scope\n   118вҶ’\n   119вҶ’Building the **streamer server only** (single binary). Mocked auth with login/password (real users in SQLite, but no email verification, no OAuth вҖ” just username+passwordвҶ’JWT).\n   120вҶ’\n   121вҶ’### In Scope\n   122вҶ’- RTMP ingest + FFmpeg transcoding to HLS\n   123вҶ’- HLS segment serving (multi-quality)\n   124вҶ’- WebSocket chat with broadcast\n   125вҶ’- Auth: register/login with username+password, JWT tokens\n   126вҶ’- Admin API (REST, no UI)\n   127вҶ’- SQLite storage\n   128вҶ’\n   129вҶ’### Out of Scope (future)\n   130вҶ’- Discovery service (cloud catalog)\n   131вҶ’- Edge CDN nodes\n   132вҶ’- Admin React SPA\n   133вҶ’- OAuth / social login\n   134вҶ’- Installer/deployment scripts\n   135вҶ’- Content moderation system\n   136вҶ’\n   137вҶ’## Conventions\n   138вҶ’\n   139вҶ’- Use Go stdlib where possible (`net/http`, `log/slog`, `encoding/json`)\n   140вҶ’- Structured logging with `log/slog`\n   141вҶ’- Errors: wrap with `fmt.Errorf(\"context: %w\", err)`\n   142вҶ’- No frameworks вҖ” keep dependencies minimal\n   143вҶ’- Tests alongside code (`*_test.go` in same package)\n   144вҶ’- Context propagation through all handlers\n   145вҶ’- Graceful shutdown on SIGINT/SIGTERM\n   146вҶ’",
